{"tid":965473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非洲人蛇藏身牀褥冀偷渡歐洲","createTime":"2019-01-02T05:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T05:51:21.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7bc3d058bee9250b89e35be8b614bacde1a8280","tid":965473,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190102/_2019010212440042141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190102%2F_2019010212440042141.jpg&h=c1d546f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西班牙邊防人員周日（30日）在北非屬地梅利利亞（Melilla）至摩洛哥間的檢查站，發現一輛載有兩張彈簧牀褥的白色客貨車，由於牀褥擺放在車頂，引起邊防人員起疑，懷疑有內藏人蛇或走私物品，遂將牀褥取下並用刀割開檢查，結果發現兩名人蛇躺在牀褥內。<br />\n<br />\n由邊防人員拍攝的紀錄畫面可見，兩張牀褥被擺放到地上時，邊防人員小心地將床墊割開，有兩名非裔男子藏身其中。其中一人被發現時似仍睡眼惺忪，不時以手指揉眼，另一人雙掌合十放在胸前。<br />\n<br />\n片段由西班牙參議員Jon Inarritu在Twitter上分享，並指出若當局持續無所作為，類似情事仍會在歐洲南部邊境發生，擔心以後會有類似手段偷運人蛇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/901102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F901102&d=8bpNXnFkE57gNuvy2jcr2bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6ca14369\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F901102&h=1b3e4a70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/901102</a><br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JonInarritu/status/1079419230959927296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJonInarritu%2Fstatus%2F1079419230959927296&d=8bpNXnFkE57gNuvy2jcr2bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f1d7c6d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJonInarritu%2Fstatus%2F1079419230959927296&h=0c82a8c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JonInarritu/status/1079419230959927296</a>"},{"pid":"cd290399475e577b804a654032fc809cec761419","tid":965473,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"個size咁撚怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一睇都知唔係正常床褥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f482811f7aa3493c00de6c97ed08badcf334715","tid":965473,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsLAJj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsLAJj2.jpg&h=830d9400&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}